failing stage was the JVM runtime `:test` lane for `xalan:xalan:2.7.3`. In `human-intervention-logs/xalan:xalan:2.7.3/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-02T00-28-13-906663Z.log`, the reproduce run fails before native-image execution with `NoClassDefFoundError` / `ClassNotFoundException` for `org/apache/xml/serializer/SerializerTrace` and `org/apache/xml/serializer/OutputPropertiesFactory`, causing 3 `XalanTest` failures and `:tckTest` to exit with code 1. The preserved branch contains a candidate fix that adds `xalan:serializer:2.7.3` to the test module and restores the missing `2.7.3` reachability metadata; `human-intervention-logs/xalan:xalan:2.7.3/metadata-fix/codex.log` shows `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=xalan:xalan:2.7.3` and `checkMetadataFiles` succeeding on the preserved commit. Metrics for that run are recorded as success in `stats/xalan/xalan/2.7.3/execution-metrics.json`, but dynamic-access coverage is unavailable (`N/A`).\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/xalan:xalan:2.7.3/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-02T00-28-13-906663Z.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/xalan:xalan:2.7.3/metadata-fix/codex.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/xalan:xalan:2.7.3/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Review the preserved branch diff, especially `tests/src/xalan/xalan/2.7.3/build.gradle` and `metadata/xalan/xalan/2.7.3/reachability-metadata.json`.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=xalan:xalan:2.7.3` and `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=xalan:xalan:2.7.3` from that branch to confirm the fix in a clean environment.\\n3. If the rerun is green, submit the preserved changes through the normal human-intervention follow-up path.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":474734,\"cached_input_tokens\":395648,\"output_tokens\":7063,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":2727}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
